<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our Platform!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #0056b3;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #0056b3;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: #004494;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>
    <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We are excited to have you on board!</p>
    <p>At our platform, we offer a wide range of events tailored to your interests. Whether you're looking for professional conferences, fun social gatherings, or educational workshops, we have something for everyone.</p>
    <p>Explore our upcoming events, book your tickets, and stay connected with the community. We are committed to providing you with the best experience possible.</p>
    <p><a href="<%= verificationLink %>">Verify Your Email</a></p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team. We are here to help you make the most of your experience.</p>
    <p>Looking forward to seeing you at our events!</p>
    <p>Best Regards,<br>The [Your Platform] Team</p>
    <p><a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>">Return to Our Site</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
